dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.commonstructure.resourceconsumption.executiontime

Interface IExecutionTime

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAnalyzedExecutionTime, IMeasuredExecutionTime, IRoughEstimateOfExecutionTime, ISimulatedExecutionTime

    public interface IExecutionTime
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IExecutionTime: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Base class for several means how to describe the ExecutionTime of software. The required context information is provided through this class.
